a pure-functional analog of pytorch's Tensor.grad_fn graph in lean 4, with mutual
inductive Tensor and GradFn replacing mutable graph nodes and a backward pass that
returns gradients as a value instead of mutating each tensor's .grad field.

trained end-to-end on microGPT, the weights are bit-identical to the python
reference.
